Gitpod Workspace Setup: Initialize AWS CLI and Terraform.
Terraform Configuration Files:
main.tf: Defines AWS provider and region.
s3.tf: Defines the S3 bucket resource.
Initialize Terraform: Run terraform init to initialize the Terraform working directory.
Configure AWS CLI: Set AWS credentials using aws configure or environment variables.
Apply the Terraform Configuration: Run terraform apply to create the S3 bucket.
Verify: Check AWS for the newly created S3 bucket.
Cleanup: Use terraform destroy to delete resources.